        "name": "MF: turbulence and hemolysis sub-model selection justified against published literature for blood pump CFD",
        "description": "The choice of turbulence closure (SST k-ω or equivalent) and hemolysis damage accumulation model (power-law, linear, or equivalent) must be justified by reference to at least two peer-reviewed publications demonstrating applicability to centrifugal blood pump CFD at the Reynolds numbers encountered in the COU."
      },
